    "After obtaining this relationship-based essay representation, LSTM with average pooling is employed to generate the overall score.",
    "This architecture differs from the aforementioned coherence modeling approaches in that coherence is embedded directly into the essay representation, rather than treating coherence information as supplementary input to the scoring model.",
